[DhtmlXQ_comment7_42]黑方先手。[/DhtmlXQ_comment7_42]
[DhtmlXQ_comment8_34]红方残相，黑方好走。[/DhtmlXQ_comment8_34]
[DhtmlXQ_comment9_21]如改走炮五进四，变化见下局第二种走法。[/DhtmlXQ_comment9_21]
[DhtmlXQ_comment9_42]双方均势。[/DhtmlXQ_comment9_42]
[DhtmlXQ_comment10_19]补仕待变，也可改走车二进九，见变例。[/DhtmlXQ_comment10_19]
[DhtmlXQ_comment10_22]如改走车2进1，红方优势，见变例。[/DhtmlXQ_comment10_22]
